comment._content: NYT of February 1, 1916 select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F2071EF9355C1373... mentions that State Senator Charles O'Connor Hennessey of Bergen County was running for the Democratic gubernatorial slot in New Jersey.

comment.author: 23103743@N05
comment._content: A photo from the Haworth, NJ website of Charles O’Connor Hennessy looks to be the same man, although considerably older.
